This systematic review is based on the all authentic data and findings from WHO and associated research. Based on the current issue of corona infection the published data is analyzed with respect to the reproduction number of corona, symptoms shown by the patients admitted in the hospitals, diagnostic procedure and available clinical trial in vitro study. Reproductive number (Ro) was calculated by using the formula \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
